  "detailed_description": "<h1>♥♥ ADD IN WISHLIST!! ♥♥</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185760/extras/91fecccf7b712bc438f1d90ae51996b5.poster.avif?t=1774431807\" width=600 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185760/extras/91fecccf7b712bc438f1d90ae51996b5.webm?t=1774431807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185760/extras/91fecccf7b712bc438f1d90ae51996b5.mp4?t=1774431807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>\"Under the Sky World\" is an orthodox casual RPG game.<br>Players are in the era of the popular virtual world,<br>One day, by chance, I entered the most popular game \"Under the Sky World\"!<br>When I entered, I accidentally found that the game was invaded by a virus.<br>Players need to find evil hackers and stop this virtual world from being destroyed!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185760/extras/8eff6499bb79bcd16233db3132f799ee.poster.avif?t=1774431807\" width=600 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185760/extras/8eff6499bb79bcd16233db3132f799ee.webm?t=1774431807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185760/extras/8eff6499bb79bcd16233db3132f799ee.mp4?t=1774431807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>KARIN</strong><br>It is Karine's avatar in SW, with cheating item given by her father.<br>When she was playing, she found that SW was invaded by hackers. <br>Can KARIN successfully save the world?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185760/extras/ebf57c50fd63655e9baf6ddf0a1a064d.webp?t=1774431807\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185760/extras/ebf57c50fd63655e9baf6ddf0a1a064d.poster.avif?t=1774431807\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=200 /></picture></span><br><br><strong>SAORI</strong><br>She is Karine's good friend at school. <br>She was fascinated by Woutube and started to be a streamer.<br>She has a NEET brother, and she is disgusted with such a brother.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185760/extras/f7176ba6c2680b49dc5e94b1c4f169ee.poster.avif?t=1774431807\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185760/extras/f7176ba6c2680b49dc5e94b1c4f169ee.webm?t=1774431807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185760/extras/f7176ba6c2680b49dc5e94b1c4f169ee.mp4?t=1774431807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>MIRIN</strong><br>An agent entrusted to enter the SW to find the source of the virus.<br>Meet KARIN in SW, and regard her as a strong enemy.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185760/extras/4713da25dbad4d723a0f68194e8e8737.poster.avif?t=1774431807\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185760/extras/4713da25dbad4d723a0f68194e8e8737.webm?t=1774431807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2185760/extras/975902a0ea7471c5fa560